data.description: Come home to this beautiful home in Lennar's Heritage Solaire upscale Active 55+ community. This beautifully designed home showcases like a model home with its plantation shutters, model white tile floors, modern ceiling pendant lights & 10' ceilings. The great room features custom remote control white panels that can also be voice controlled with Alexa.  The honeywell programmed thermostat can also be controlled by Alexa as this is a smart home ready for great technical upgrades.  Your open concept kitchen offers a huge island with granite waterfall counters, 2 ovens, white, soft-close cabinets with roll-out drawers, tile backsplash and a walk-in pantry. Your 2 junior ensuites, an office with custom cabinets and desks along with  custom sliding barn doors for privacy.  The master suite will not disappoint with its custom designed walk in closet and sitting area. Home is close to parks, golfing, trails, dining, world-class shopping, Nugget Market, Farmers' Market, freeway, medical. Enjoy the Clubhouse pool/spa, pickle ball, tennis, Bocce ball, BBQ, TV & activity room, fitness center, kitchen and wine bar,  community garden, amphitheater.  HOA maintains front yards. Solar community w/Roseville Electric Utilities.
